                                            Precio del oro (USD){{lang.wrapperdash.preciooro}}
                                        </h3>
                                </div>

                                <div>
                                    <canvas id="lineChart" height="46" width="100%"></canvas>
                                </div>

                                <div class="m-t-md">
                                    <small class="pull-right">
